{
  "stem": "9091.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So apparently they decided to go and be with my grandmother there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went there to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then the bombardment of Warsaw started, and it was a very hard time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The bombardment was very heavy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from what I was told later, I remembered that too, that they apparently bombed Warsaw with [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] burning bombs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the whole city was burning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as soon as we went into one building for shelter, it was bombed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we ran out from one building, ran to the other building.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by the time we came to the other building, the other building was burning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we were running like a mouse from one hole to the other, and the whole city was running.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you saw dead people and children all over the streets.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember a little child sitting and crying, mommy, mommy, and the mother was dead [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And dead were-- dead people were all over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And destruction was all over [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we stayed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But finally, the-- the-- the bombardment ended, and then we decided to go back to our apartment.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we-- we were waiting for letters from-- from-- from our father, and they didn't come.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know that he was already dead by that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Since my mother-- we didn't have any money, and my father was gone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother decided that she'll would take me, six years old, and my-- my younger brother, four years old, and we know where he was supposed to be, and we would go look for him there.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Of course, my grandmother-- my mother's mother-- was very much against it.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
